STEP 56 CHECK_ANSWER
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH all
REPLY QR RA NOERROR
SECTION QUESTION
nx1.example.com. IN A
SECTION ANSWER
SECTION AUTHORITY
example.com.	IN NS	ns.example.com.
SECTION ADDITIONAL
ns.example.com.		IN 	A	1.2.3.4
ENTRY_END

